Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (133 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (133 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case
